 *                        |   +---------------------------+   +---------------------------+  |
 *  +-----------------+   |   |   +--------+  +--------+  |   |   +--------+  +--------+  |  |  +-------------+
 *  |                 | s1|   |   |        |s2|        |  | s3|   |        |s4|        |  |  |s5|             |
 *  |  Cell_clnt c[0] |-+-|---|>--|> Cell1 |--|> Cell2 |--+---|>--|> Cell3 |--|> Cell4 |--+--|--|> Cell_serv1 |
 *  |            c[1] |-+ |   |   |        |  |        |  |   |   |        |  |        |  |  |  |             |
 *  +-----------------+ | |   |   +--------+  +--------+  |   |   +--------+  +--------+  |  |  +-------------+
 *                      | |   |       tComp11 comp11      |   |       tComp12 comp12      |  |
 *                      | |   +---------------------------+   +---------------------------+  |
 *                      | |                          tComp3 Comp1                            |
 *                      | +------------------------------------------------------------------+
 *                      |
 *                      | +------------------------------------------------------------------+
 *                      | |   +---------------------------+   +---------------------------+  |
 *                      | |   |   +--------+  +--------+  |   |   +--------+  +--------+  |  |  +-------------+
 *                      | |   |   |        |s2|        |  | s3|   |        |s4|        |  |  |s5|             |
 *                      +-|>--|>--|> Cell1 |--|> Cell2 |--+---|>--|> Cell3 |--|> Cell4 |--+--|--|> Cell_serv2 |
 *                        |   |   |        |  |        |  |   |   |        |  |        |  |  |  |             |
 *                        |   |   +--------+  +--------+  |   |   +--------+  +--------+  |  |  +-------------+
 *                        |   |       tComp11 comp11      |   |       tComp12 comp12      |  |
 *                        |   +---------------------------+   +---------------------------+  |
